sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Intel Corp ( INTC ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 2.0%.
Year to date, Intel Corp registers a 16.2% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Boeing ( BA ), trading down 1.0%.
Boeing is showing a gain of 14.6% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Home Depot ( HD ), trading down 0.6%, and Cisco Systems ( CSCO ), trading up 1.2% on the day.
